      <p class="mb-0">This is a practice app to learn functionality and much of the formatting has been skipped for the sake of time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-4">
      <h4 class="fst-italic">From the Archives</h4>
      <ol class="list-unstyled mb-0">
        <li><a href="#">March 2023</a></li>
